OL,3,CO'Neill at centre of police probe into
OL,4,Calleged misconduct in public office
OL,6,FThe PSNI is investigating an
OL,7,Fallegation of misconduct in public
OL,8,Foffice by the First Minister Michelle
OL,9,FO'Neill and Alliance MLA Paula
OL,10,FBradshaw.
OL,12,FTUV Leader Jim Allister revealed the
OL,13,Finvestigation ahead of a Stormont
OL,14,Fdebate in which his colleague MLA
OL,15,FTimothy Gaston could be barred from
OL,16,Fthe assembly for two days for comments
OL,17,Fhe made at a committee in October 2024.
