OL,3,CO'Neill at centre of police probe into
OL,4,Calleged misconduct in public office
OL,6,FIn a statement, police confirmed: "The
OL,7,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland
OL,8,Freceived correspondence concerning an
OL,9,Fallegation of misconduct in public
OL,10,Foffice in October 2024. Enquiries
OL,11,Fremain ongoing."
OL,13,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,14,Fhere.
OL,16,FIt comes as Mr Gaston has been found
OL,17,Fto have breached the Assembly Members
OL,18,FCode of Conduct during stormy
OL,19,Fexchanges at the committee.
