OL,3,CO'Neill at centre of police probe into
OL,4,Calleged misconduct in public office
OL,6,FA complaint was made against the North
OL,7,FAntrim representative following a
OL,8,Fmeeting of the Executive Office
OL,9,Fcommittee on October 23 2024.
OL,11,FThere were tense scenes between Mr
OL,12,FGaston and committee chairwoman Paula
OL,13,FBradshaw around an allegation Ms
OL,14,FBradshaw met First Minister Michelle
OL,15,FO'Neill before she appeared at the
OL,16,Fcommittee to give evidence.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/17
