OL,3,CO'Neill at centre of police probe into
OL,4,Calleged misconduct in public office
OL,6,FFormer independent Assembly
OL,7,FCommissioner for Standards Dr Melissa
OL,8,FMcCullough, who investigated the
OL,9,Fcomplaint, concluded that Mr Gaston
OL,10,Fhad breached Rule 15 of the code.
OL,12,FShe found he had engaged in behaviour
OL,13,Fthat constituted an "unreasonable and
OL,14,Fexcessive personal attack" on Ms
OL,15,FBradshaw.
