OL,3,CO'Neill at centre of police probe into
OL,4,Calleged misconduct in public office
OL,6,FThe Committee on Standards and
OL,7,FPrivileges upheld the complaint and is
OL,8,Frecommending that Mr Gaston be
OL,9,Fsanctioned by being excluded from
OL,10,FAssembly proceedings for two sitting
OL,11,Fdays.
OL,13,FCommittee chairwoman Cathy Mason MLA
OL,14,Fsaid its members are "firmly of the
OL,15,Fview that Mr Gaston's behaviour was
OL,16,Finconsistent with the standards
OL,17,Frequired".
OL,26,@vD@VOUyD@IO]
