OL,3,CO'Neill at centre of police probe into
OL,4,Calleged misconduct in public office
OL,6,F"It is vitally important that members
OL,7,Frespect the authority of committee
OL,8,Fchairpersons and uphold the rules and
OL,9,Fprotocols which ensure the proper
OL,10,Ffunctioning of Assembly committees,"
OL,11,Fshe added.
OL,13,FTUV leader Jim Allister claimed the
OL,14,FAssembly has "stooped to a new low",
OL,15,Fadding it was "absurd beyond words".
OL,17,FSpeaking to media at Parliament
OL,18,FBuildings on Monday, he also indicated
OL,19,Fthat potential legal action has not
OL,20,Fbeen ruled out.
