OL,3,CO'Neill at centre of police probe into
OL,4,Calleged misconduct in public office
OL,6,FHe added: "In circumstances where
OL,7,Fthere is apparently an ongoing police
OL,8,Finquiry into these matters, it is
OL,9,Fwholly disproportionate and
OL,10,Finappropriate for this Assembly to
OL,11,Ftoday to proceed to sanction anyone
OL,12,Funless or until those proceedings are
OL,13,Fcomplete."
OL,15,FThe DUP has indicated its MLAs will
OL,16,Fvote against the sanction, and the UUP
OL,17,Fhas urged that the process is paused.
OL,19,FDUP leader Gavin Robinson said he
OL,20,Fbelieves the findings of the
OL,21,Fcommissioner are "irrational".
