OL,3,CO'Neill at centre of police probe into
OL,4,Calleged misconduct in public office
OL,6,F"I engaged in political discourse, and
OL,7,Fat times robust exchanges with many,
OL,8,Fand I think the public out there would
OL,9,Fbe more interested in elected
OL,10,Frepresentatives in this place
OL,11,Fdelivering for them."
OL,13,FIn a statement, a UUP spokesperson
OL,14,Fsaid that the sanction process into Mr
OL,15,FGaston should be paused until the PSNI
OL,16,Finquiry fully concludes: "This upholds
OL,17,Fdue process and ensures all facts are
OL,18,Fconsidered.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@UO]
