OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F442A1770068146
OL,3,CO'Neill at centre of police probe into
OL,4,Calleged misconduct in public office
OL,6,F"Proceeding prematurely would render
OL,7,Fthe sanction disproportionate and
OL,8,Fpotentially unjust, and we urge the
OL,9,FSpeaker to suspend proceedings pending
OL,10,Fthe inquiry's determination.
OL,12,F"This situation raises profound
OL,13,Fquestions about the integrity of the
OL,14,FAssembly's entire standards process
OL,15,Fand highlights the pressing need for
OL,16,Fcomprehensive reform."
OL,18,FAn Alliance spokesperson said: "Only
OL,19,Fone MLA has been found in breach of
OL,20,Fthe Code of Conduct in this case, and
OL,21,Fthat is Timothy Gaston.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/17
