OL,3,CO'Neill at centre of police probe into
OL,4,Calleged misconduct in public office
OL,6,F"Statements from the TUV this morning
OL,7,Fare nothing more than misleading
OL,8,Fconjecture and distraction. Such
OL,9,Fcommentary only further undermines
OL,10,Fstandards in the Assembly.
OL,12,F"Unlike others, we respect due process
OL,13,Fand the embargo that is in place.
OL,14,FHowever, once the report is published,
OL,15,Fwe would encourage people to read it
OL,16,Fin full. It will then become clear
OL,17,FPaula Bradshaw has no case to answer
OL,18,Fbut rather has been subject to
OL,19,Fbullying, unfounded allegations and
OL,20,Fdisruptive behaviour.
